{"_id":"EARTauto01","name":"EA — Critical Injuries (Automata)","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","description":"Roll D66 when an Automata suffers a critical injury.","formula":"d66","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"REARTauto0100","type":"text","text":"<strong>Scratched Paint</strong> — None.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0101","type":"text","text":"<strong>Emergency Shutdown</strong> — None.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0102","type":"text","text":"<strong>Reset Engaged</strong> — None.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0103","type":"text","text":"<strong>Injured Foot Bracket</strong> — Mobility -2 and can't run until a Medical roll is made.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0104","type":"text","text":"<strong>Damaged Visual Receptors</strong> — Observation and Ranged Combat -2 until a Machinery roll is made.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0105","type":"text","text":"<strong>Shorted Out Stabilizers</strong> — Mobility -2. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0106","type":"text","text":"<strong>Comms Down</strong> — Can't communicate with other pilots or outside assistance. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[21,21],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0107","type":"text","text":"<strong>Damaged Leg Joints</strong> — To run becomes a Slow Action. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[22,22],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0108","type":"text","text":"<strong>Destroyed Hand</strong> — Can't use the hand. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[23,23],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0109","type":"text","text":"<strong>Broken Targeting Systems</strong> — Ranged Combat -2 until Machinery is rolled. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[24,24],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0110","type":"text","text":"<strong>Disconnected Power Supply</strong> — Your Automata shuts down. Repair: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[25,25],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0111","type":"text","text":"<strong>Arm Dislocated</strong> — Can't use the arm. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[26,26],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0112","type":"text","text":"<strong>Blown Thrusters</strong> — Can only take a single Slow Action. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[31,31],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0113","type":"text","text":"<strong>Mechanical Fire</strong> — One point of damage every Mobility and Ranged Combat roll. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[32,32],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0114","type":"text","text":"<strong>Infected Systems</strong> — Gain Horror Toxicosis. Repair: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[33,33],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0115","type":"text","text":"<strong>Radiated Systems</strong> — Gain Seraph Radiation. Repair: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[34,34],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0116","type":"text","text":"<strong>Destroyed Joint Systems</strong> — Automata can't move. Repair: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[35,35],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0117","type":"text","text":"<strong>Broken Arm</strong> — Can't use the arm. Repair: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[36,36],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0118","type":"text","text":"<strong>Broken Leg</strong> — Can't run, only crawl. Repair: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[41,41],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0119","type":"text","text":"<strong>Crushed Foot Joint</strong> — Can't run, only crawl. Repair: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[42,42],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0120","type":"text","text":"<strong>Crushed Elbow Joint</strong> — Can't use the arm. Repair: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[43,43],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0121","type":"text","text":"<strong>Exposed Support Systems</strong> — Endurance and Mobility -2. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[44,44],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0122","type":"text","text":"<strong>Impaled Chest</strong> — One point of damage every Mobility and Close Combat roll. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[45,45],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0123","type":"text","text":"<strong>Shatter Frame</strong> — Pilot rolls for Critical Injury. Repair: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[46,46],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0124","type":"text","text":"<strong>Leg Overload</strong> — Can't run, only crawl, Mobility -2. Repair: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[51,51],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0125","type":"text","text":"<strong>Arm Overload</strong> — Can't use the arm. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[52,52],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0126","type":"text","text":"<strong>Busted Hydraulics</strong> — To run becomes a Slow Action. Repair: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[53,53],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0127","type":"text","text":"<strong>Severed Arm</strong> — Can't use the arm. Repair: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[54,54],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0128","type":"text","text":"<strong>Severed Leg</strong> — Can't run, only crawl. Repair: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[55,55],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0129","type":"text","text":"<strong>Synchronization System Destroyed</strong> — The Automata goes completely still. If not treated in time, permanent. Repair: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[56,56],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0130","type":"text","text":"<strong>Life Support Offline</strong> — Stability -2. Repair: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[61,61],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0131","type":"text","text":"<strong>Major Ego Degradation</strong> — Ego -2. Repair: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[62,62],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0132","type":"text","text":"<strong>Engine Destruction</strong> — The main engine and Automata are destroyed. Repair: max Durability shifts.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[63,63],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0133","type":"text","text":"<strong>Destroyed Head</strong> — The Automata is destroyed. Repair: max Durability shifts.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[64,64],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0134","type":"text","text":"<strong>Collapsed Cockpit</strong> — Automata destroyed. Pilot rolls for Critical Injury. Repair: max Durability shifts.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[65,65],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTauto0135","type":"text","text":"<strong>Destroyed Cockpit</strong> — The pilot is killed instantly.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[66,66],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}}],"flags":{}}
{"_id":"EARTpilot01","name":"EA — Critical Injuries (Pilot)","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","description":"Roll D66 when a pilot suffers a critical injury.","formula":"d66","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"REARTpilot0100","type":"text","text":"<strong>Winded</strong> — None.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0101","type":"text","text":"<strong>Stunned</strong> — None.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0102","type":"text","text":"<strong>Crippling Pain</strong> — None.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[13,13],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0103","type":"text","text":"<strong>Sprained Ankle</strong> — Mobility -2 and movement is a Slow Action until a Medical roll is made.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0104","type":"text","text":"<strong>Blood in Eyes</strong> — Observation and Ranged Combat -2 until a Medical roll is made.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0105","type":"text","text":"<strong>Concussion</strong> — Mobility -2. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0106","type":"text","text":"<strong>Severed Ear</strong> — Observation -2. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[21,21],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0107","type":"text","text":"<strong>Broken Toes</strong> — Movement becomes a Slow Action. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[22,22],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0108","type":"text","text":"<strong>Broken Hand</strong> — Hand cannot be used. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[23,23],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0109","type":"text","text":"<strong>Knocked Out Teeth</strong> — Persuasion -2. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[24,24],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0110","type":"text","text":"<strong>Impaled Thigh</strong> — Movement becomes a Slow Action. Healing: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[25,25],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0111","type":"text","text":"<strong>Slashed Shoulder</strong> — Arm cannot be used. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[26,26],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0112","type":"text","text":"<strong>Broken Nose</strong> — Persuasion and Observation -1. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[31,31],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0113","type":"text","text":"<strong>Crotch Hit</strong> — One point of damage for every Mobility or Melee roll made. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[32,32],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0114","type":"text","text":"<strong>Broken Ribs</strong> — Mobility and Observation -2. Healing: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[33,33],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0115","type":"text","text":"<strong>Gouged Eye</strong> — Ranged Combat and Observation -2. Healing: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[34,34],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0116","type":"text","text":"<strong>Busted Kneecap</strong> — Movement becomes a Slow Action. Healing: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[35,35],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0117","type":"text","text":"<strong>Broken Arm</strong> — Arm cannot be used. Healing: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[36,36],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0118","type":"text","text":"<strong>Broken Leg</strong> — Can't run, only crawl. Healing: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[41,41],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0119","type":"text","text":"<strong>Crushed Foot</strong> — Can't run, only crawl. Healing: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[42,42],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0120","type":"text","text":"<strong>Crushed Elbow</strong> — Arm cannot be used. Healing: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[43,43],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0121","type":"text","text":"<strong>Punctured Lung</strong> — LETHAL — Time: Shift. Stamina and Mobility -2. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[44,44],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0122","type":"text","text":"<strong>Bleeding Gut</strong> — LETHAL — Time: Shift. One point of damage every Mobility or Melee roll. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[45,45],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0123","type":"text","text":"<strong>Ruptured Intestines</strong> — LETHAL — Time: Shift. Infected wound Virulence 6. Healing: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[46,46],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0124","type":"text","text":"<strong>Busted Kidney</strong> — LETHAL — Time: Day. Mobility -2 and movement is a Slow Action. Healing: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[51,51],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0125","type":"text","text":"<strong>Severed Arm Artery</strong> — LETHAL — Time: -1 Stretch. Arm cannot be used. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[52,52],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0126","type":"text","text":"<strong>Severed Leg Artery</strong> — LETHAL — Time: -1 Stretch. Movement becomes a Slow Action. Healing: D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[53,53],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0127","type":"text","text":"<strong>Severed Arm</strong> — LETHAL — Time: -1 Shift. Arm cannot be used. Healing: Permanent.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[54,54],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0128","type":"text","text":"<strong>Severed Leg</strong> — LETHAL — Time: -1 Shift. Can't run, only crawl. Healing: Permanent.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[55,55],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0129","type":"text","text":"<strong>Cracked Spine</strong> — Paralyzed from neck down. If not treated in time, permanent. Healing: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[56,56],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0130","type":"text","text":"<strong>Ruptured Jugular</strong> — LETHAL — Time: -1 Round. Stamina -1. Healing: 2D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[61,61],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0131","type":"text","text":"<strong>Ruptured Aorta</strong> — LETHAL — Time: -2 Rounds. Stamina -2. Healing: 3D6.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[62,62],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0132","type":"text","text":"<strong>Disemboweled</strong> — LETHAL — Instant death.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[63,63],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0133","type":"text","text":"<strong>Crushed Skull</strong> — LETHAL — Your story ends here.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[64,64],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0134","type":"text","text":"<strong>Pierced Head</strong> — LETHAL — You die immediately.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[65,65],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"REARTpilot0135","type":"text","text":"<strong>Impaled Heart</strong> — LETHAL — Your heart beats for the last time.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[66,66],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}}],"flags":{}}
{"_id":"EATraumaTable1","name":"EA — Permanent Trauma","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","description":"Roll D6 when Permanent Trauma is triggered (Stress 10 + Breakdown, failed Empathy roll).","formula":"1d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"RTtrauma00","type":"text","text":"<strong>Lucky</strong> — No lasting trauma.","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"RTtrauma01","type":"text","text":"<strong>Addiction</strong> — You develop a required habit. If you ignore it across an entire Shift, your Stress Level increases by 1 and you cannot alleviate Stress until your habit is indulged.","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"RTtrauma02","type":"text","text":"<strong>Nightmares</strong> — Make an Empathy roll when you sleep. If the roll fails, your Stress Level increases by 1. You cannot relieve Stress for a full day after such a nightmare.","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"RTtrauma03","type":"text","text":"<strong>Depression</strong> — Every day, make an Empathy roll. If you fail, your Stress Level increases by 1 and you can't relieve Stress until the next day.","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"RTtrauma04","type":"text","text":"<strong>Phobia</strong> — Something related to the incident terrifies you. Your Stress increases by 1 when initially coming into Short Range with your phobia. Induces a Panic roll after being in Short Range for more than a single round.","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"_id":"RTtrauma05","type":"text","text":"<strong>Amnesia</strong> — Reduce all points in a single Skill (your choice) to 0 until your trauma is treated.","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"flags":{}}],"flags":{}}
